snippet.title: Mortal Shell - Rotten Autumn: Free Update Out Now | PS4
snippet.description:
Something sinister has arrived in Fallgrim. Possess the Rotten Autumn update and access 10 new shell shades, a brand new photo mode, and an alternative boss OST by Rotting Christ. Download for Free today!

Download Now: 
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP3639-CUSA16364_00-0000000000000001
